  "instructions": [
    "Heat coconut oil in a large skillet over medium-high heat.",
    "Add onion, bell pepper, and carrots to the skillet. Cook until the vegetables are tender, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add grape leaves, cinnamon, allspice, brown sugar, and ginger to the skillet. Cook for 2 minutes.",
    "Stir in salt and black pepper. ",
    "Transfer the skillet to the oven and bake at 375°F (190°C) for 15 minutes.",
    "Remove the skillet from the oven and top with chopped scallions.",
    "Serve hot."
  ],
